He told the Daily Mirror  that the girls were obsessed with watching the series, which included a euthanasia plot featuring long-standing character Hayley Cropper, played by Julie Hesmondhalgh.

In the soap, Hayley took her own life after a battle with untreatable pancreatic cancer. The storyline ran for several episodes before her death scene, which was watched by 10.2million viewers when it was screened in January.

