Caller was bailed pending further investigation, but was charged with assisting the suicide of another by Lincolnshire Police today.

She will appear at Lincoln Magistrates' Court on October 16. 

Police were called to the rented flat Miss Crossman lived in at 10.40am on January 15 where they discovered her lifeless body. 

